**ASX Buy-Back Notification Summary (ORA: ORORA LIMITED)**  

- **Type of Buy-Back**: On-market  
- **Total Buy-Back Program**: Up to 134,349,993 shares (10% of issued capital)  
- **Dates**: Active from 24/12/2024 to 23/12/2025  
- **Daily Activity (19/06/2025)**: 1,000,000 shares repurchased at average ~AUD 1.79/share  
- **Cumulative Buy-Back**: 58,800,894 shares repurchased (AUD 120.8M total consideration)  
- **Price Range**: Highest paid AUD 2.50 (31/12/2024); lowest AUD 1.67 (07/04/2025)  
- **Broker**: UBS/Jarden executing the buy-back  
- **Approval**: No shareholder approval required  

**Material Impact**: Active capital management, reducing shares outstanding by up to 10%. Market conditions dictate execution.
